  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "    Welcome to Torch, the playable Unity-based tabletop strategy war game
    combat simulator! This tool is meant to teach you the basics of how to using
    the Dungeons and Dragons 5th edition combat system by letting you create your
    own characters, and run them through pre-made encounters that will test your
    strategic mind!\r\n    Game mechanics will be introduced in each combat encounter,
    so if you ever feel confused about the gameplay, you can always click the ? icon
    in the top right of the screen to see an explanation of what mechanics are being
    introduced in the current encounter or menu. You can also press 'esc' to go to
    the tutorial menu, which will have a list of every combat mechanic sorted by
    the order they are introduced in, so take a look if you ever need a reminder!\r\n   
    I hope you have fun and learn a lot!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
